#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/magic_items/helm_of_brilliance.md:6
msgid "# Helm of Brilliance _Wondrous item, very rare (requires attunement)_"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/magic_items/helm_of_brilliance.md:9
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"This dazzling helm is set with 1d10 diamonds, 2d10 rubies, 3d10 fire opals, "
"and 4d10 opals. Any gem pried from the helm crumbles to dust. When all the "
"gems are removed or destroyed, the helm loses its magic.    \n"
"You gain the following benefits while wearing it:\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/magic_items/helm_of_brilliance.md:14
msgid ""
"You can use an action to cast one of the following spells (save DC 18), "
"using one of the helm's gems of the specified type as a component: "
"**_daylight_** (opal), **_fireball_** (fire opal), **_prismatic spray_** "
"(diamond), or **_wall of fire_** (ruby). The gem is destroyed when the spell "
"is cast and disappears from the helm."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/magic_items/helm_of_brilliance.md:14
msgid ""
"As long as it has at least one diamond, the helm emits dim light in a "
"30-foot radius when at least one undead is within that area. Any undead that "
"starts its turn in that area takes 1d6 radiant damage."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/magic_items/helm_of_brilliance.md:14
msgid ""
"As long as the helm has at least one ruby, you have resistance to fire "
"damage."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/magic_items/helm_of_brilliance.md:14
msgid ""
"As long as the helm has at least one fire opal, you can use an action and "
"speak a command word to cause one weapon you are holding to burst into "
"flames. The flames emit bright light in a 10-foot radius and dim light for "
"an additional 10 feet. The flames are harmless to you and the weapon. When "
"you hit with an attack using the blazing weapon, the target takes an extra "
"1d6 fire damage. The flames last until you use a bonus action to speak the "
"command word again or until you drop or stow the weapon."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/magic_items/helm_of_brilliance.md:15
msgid ""
"Roll a d20 if you are wearing the helm and take fire damage as a result of "
"failing a saving throw against a spell. On a roll of 1, the helm emits beams "
"of light from its remaining gems. Each creature within 60 feet of the helm "
"other than you must succeed on a DC 17 Dexterity saving throw or be struck "
"by a beam, taking radiant damage equal to the number of gems in the "
"helm. The helm and its gems are then destroyed."
msgstr ""
